These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, sprite
There 3 different types of food: apple, tomato, watermelon
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, scientist, security-guard
House: craftsman, cottage, art-deco
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, march, november
The people have 3 different hobbies: singing, filmmaking, collecting
 1. the person who's hobby is collecting is the scientist##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the cottage house##1
 3. the accountant is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 4. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far right##1
 5. the scientist is the person eating apple##1
 6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 7. the craftsman house is the person drinking sprite##1
 8. the person eating tomato is in the middle##1
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
10. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2       |    3     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | sprite        | lemonade |
| Food          | watermelon    | tomato        | apple    |
| Job   | security-guard        | accountant        | scientist    |
| House           | art-deco        | craftsman    | cottage   |
| Birthday         | march    | november | january |
| Hobby     | filmmaking     | singing          | collecting     |

