.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-1-2::.
3 different pets are kept: ferret, chinchilla, goat
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, juice, almond-milk
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, satire, zombie
House: townhouse, colonial, futuristic
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, september, november
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, motorbike, train
1. the person drinking lemonade is the futuristic house##1
2. the townhouse house is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the ferret is the person driving the motorbike##1
6. the futuristic house is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
7. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
8. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
9. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |         3          |
| Pet         | goat    | ferret     | chinchilla            |
| Beverage           | juice | lemonade | almond-milk |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | satire      | zombie             |
| House   | townhouse | futuristic     | colonial             |
| Birthday         | september  | november       | april           |
| Transport     | train     | motorbike   | jet-ski            |

