.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-1-3::.
3 different games are played: bridge, canasta, scrabble
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, april, march
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, western, zombie
There are 3 different nationalities: american, canadian, german
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, juice, fanta
There are 3 different favourite colors: chestnut, grey, apricot
1. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the american is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking juice is the person watching documentary movies##1
4. the person drinking milk is on the right of the german##1
5. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
6. the person drinking fanta is the person who likes chestnut##1
7. the person drinking milk is the person watching western movies##1
8. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
9. the canadian is the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |      3       |
| Game         | scrabble  | bridge     | canasta    |
| Birthday           | april | may  | march |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie       | documentary | western      |
| Nationality   | american     | german      | canadian     |
| Beverage           | fanta          | juice      | milk   |
| Color     | chestnut          | apricot       | grey    |

