.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-1-4::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, november, october
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, boat, scooter
There are 3 different favourite colors: yellow, emerald, orange
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, marigold, bellflower
There are 3 different nationalities: american, british, german
3 different pets are kept: goat, rabbit, rat
 1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1
 2. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 3. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the american##1
 4. the person who growsdaffodil is in the middle##1
 5. the british is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
 6. the person who likes orange is the person who growsbellflower##1
 7. the owner of the rat is the person who likes yellow##1
 8. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
10. the british is the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |
| Birthday          | may | november | october        |
| Transport         | boat  | taxi   | scooter     |
| Color           | orange  | yellow | emerald |
| Flower   | bellflower  | daffodil   | marigold     |
| Nationality   | british  | american  | german      |
| Pet           | rabbit   | rat       | goat        |

