7. the person who's sport is baseball is the person drinking tea##1
8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
9. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3      |
| Food          | broccoli | mango        | raspberry  |
| Music-Genre           | soul     | dubstep | disco |
