.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Beverage      | coffee    | milk     | water         |
| House          | cottage  | art-deco    | cape-cod         |
| Cigar           | bolivar | oliveros | pall-mall          |
| Game   | scrabble    | backgammon      | mah-jongg        |
| Music-Genre   | salsa     | funk     | rock          |
| Nationality         | indian    | german | argentine |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-1-20::.
There 3 different types of food: apricot, corn, mango
The people have 3 different jobs:  lawyer, software-developer, accountant
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, almond-milk, juice
There are 3 different favourite colors: lavender, red, chestnut
3 different pets are kept: bird, cat, mouse
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, december, march
1. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is the person eating corn##1
3. the person eating mango is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person who likes red##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is the lawyer##1
6. the owner of the mouse is in the middle##1
7. the accountant is the owner of the cat##1
8. the person who likes lavender is on the far left##1
9. the software-developer is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |      3       |
| Food          | corn          | mango      | apricot      |
| Job         | accountant        | software-developer | lawyer      |
| Beverage   | sprite          | almond-milk        | juice       |
| Color   | lavender       | red   | chestnut      |
| Pet           | cat           | mouse      | bird         |
| Birthday         | march | april    | december |

 